loadout-description-LoadoutItemCig = Cool guys always have a cigarette.
loadout-description-LoadoutItemCigsGreen = A pack a day keeps the doctors at bay.
loadout-description-LoadoutItemCigsRed = A pack a day keeps the doctors at bay.
loadout-description-LoadoutItemCigsBlue = A pack a day keeps the doctors at bay.
loadout-description-LoadoutItemCigsBlack = A pack a day keeps the doctors at bay.
loadout-description-LoadoutItemPAI = A bit unstable on startup, but you won't find a more loyal friend.
loadout-description-LoadoutItemLighter = A simple lighter.
loadout-description-LoadoutItemLighterCheap = A very simple lighter.
loadout-description-LoadoutItemMatches = A box of matches.
loadout-description-LoadoutItemPlushieSharkBlue = Dive into battle alongside your aquatic ally, the Blue Shark Plushie! It's more plush than fierce, but don't underestimate its ability to inspire fear in your enemies... or at least make them laugh as they're overwhelmed by its adorableness.
loadout-description-LoadoutItemPlushieSharkPink = Unleash the power of pink with the Pink Shark Plushie! This pink predator may not have real teeth, but its sheer charm is enough to shatter anyone's resolve. Watch as your enemies melt before its cottony charm.
loadout-description-LoadoutItemPlushieSharkGrey = Introducing the Grey Shark Plushie, the apex predator of plushiness! With its sleek and modest design, this plush strikes the perfect balance between cuddly companion and sea guardian of imagination. Beware; enemies may be mesmerized by the hypnotic sway of its dorsal fin!
loadout-description-LoadoutItemPlushieCarp = Get ready for intergalactic mischief with the Purple Space Carp Plushie! A fish invader from the cosmic deep, this plush brings a dose of humor to zero gravity. From hostile waters to intergalactic guffaws, this plush paradox transcends our world.
loadout-description-LoadoutSolCommonTranslator = The most common of all translators, so much so that it can be purchased on any civilized station.
                                                 This device translates speech from Solar Common to Galactic Common.
